HEADWORD: Trubu
<hw>Tru*bu"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An
East India herring (<spn>Clupea toli</spn>) which is extensively caught
for the sake of its roe and for its flesh.</def>⟦br⟧
